---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy policy" description="Privacy policy for Travel-Îles." locale="en" alternateUrl="/confidentialite">
	<section class="container-wide legal-page">
		<header class="legal-header">
			<span class="kicker">Privacy</span>
			<h1 class="page-title">Privacy policy</h1>
		</header>

		<div class="prose">
			<h2>Data collected</h2>
			<p>Travel-Îles does not collect any personal data. The site uses no registration form, traffic analytics tool, or advertising tracking pixel.</p>

			<h2>Cookies</h2>
			<p>The site uses a single local cookie (<code>ti-cookies</code>) to store your choice regarding embedded videos. This cookie is stored in your browser and is not shared with any third party.</p>
			<p>If you accept cookies, YouTube, Vimeo, Facebook, or Instagram video players may set their own cookies. These cookies are governed by the respective privacy policies of those platforms.</p>

			<h2>Embedded videos</h2>
			<p>Videos are hosted by third-party services (YouTube, Vimeo, Facebook, Instagram). By accepting video playback, you accept the terms of use and privacy policy of those services.</p>

			<h2>Hosting</h2>
			<p>The site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect technical data (IP address, HTTP headers) for security and performance purposes. See the <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare privacy policy</a>.</p>

			<h2>Your rights</h2>
			<p>You can delete the consent cookie at any time in your browser settings. For any questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@traveliles.com">contact@traveliles.com</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.legal-page { padding-top: var(--space-12); padding-bottom: var(--space-20); }
	.legal-header { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-4); margin-bottom: var(--space-10); }
	.prose code { font-size: 0.9em; background: var(--surface-sunken); padding: 0.15em 0.4em; border-radius: var(--radius-xs); }
</style>
